trans-unit.source: The <see cref="N:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections" /> namespace contains interfaces that define collections of <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IContract" /> and <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.RemoteArgument" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: O namespace <see cref="N:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections" /> contém interfaces que definem coleções de objetos <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IContract" /> e <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.RemoteArgument" />.

trans-unit.source: Use the interfaces in the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections?displayProperty=nameWithType> namespace to implement collection classes for <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IContract> and <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.RemoteArgument> objects.
trans-unit.target: Use as interfaces a <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections?displayProperty=nameWithType> namespace para implementar a coleção de classes para <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IContract> e <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.RemoteArgument> objetos.

trans-unit.source: The interfaces in the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections?displayProperty=nameWithType> namespace are also called contracts.
trans-unit.target: Interfaces de <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections?displayProperty=nameWithType> namespace também são chamados de contratos.

trans-unit.source: All contracts derive from the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IContract> interface.
trans-unit.target: Todos os contratos derivam o <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IContract> interface.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections?displayProperty=nameWithType> namespace contains two sets of interfaces:
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections?displayProperty=nameWithType> namespace contém dois conjuntos de interfaces:

trans-unit.source: Interfaces that define generic and enumerable collections of types that implement the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IContract> interface.
trans-unit.target: Interfaces que definem coleções genéricas e enumeráveis de tipos que implementam o <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IContract> interface.

trans-unit.source: Interfaces that define enumerable collections of <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.RemoteArgument> objects.
trans-unit.target: Interfaces que definem coleções enumeráveis de <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.RemoteArgument> objetos.
